    "summary": "Radha Nikhade\nradha.nikhade@gmail.com / 06-36454451\n\nSummary\nChartered Accountant with 20+ years of broad experience in Auditing, Finance, Controlling, and Accounting featuring global clients within International organizations across Europe & Asia. \nHighlights\n\u2022\tExcellent knowledge of financial frameworks and standards like US GAAP, IFRS, Dutch GAAP & Indian GAAP. \n\u2022\tHeld various roles and responsibilities such as Audit Manager, Senior Controller & Account Manager. Managed various domains and industries such as Government sector, Construction, Banking, Petro-Chemical, Information Technology, Insurance, Automobile Industry, Telecom Industry, Steel Industry, Manufacturing, Hi -Tech, Retailers, Trading, Travel,Trust etc. \n\u2022\tExcellent knowledge of Windows office applications, Oracle, Hyperion, Exact online & SAP.\n\nEducation\n\u2022\tChartered Accountant (Law, Finance, Accountancy, Economics and Audit)\n\u2022\tBachelor of Commerce & Economics\nAccomplishments\n\u2022\tSuccessfully managed global clients and acquired new business along with recovery of long pending dues while working with SGG Management. \n\u2022\tEfficiently helped in transition from Oracle to SAP. Managed and trained the MJN shared service centre based in Philippines regarding SAP and accounting processes.\n\u2022\tBeing the first member to be absorbed in the NYSE Euronext team, was able to form accounting processes, conduct interviews for new team members and customize oracle financial. Effectively managed a complete team based out of London.\n\u2022\tEffectively managed Deloitte audit teams ranging from five to fifteen members for top most Asian organizations. Successfully worked with tight deadlines along with excellent quality of work leading to clients\u2019 satisfaction.\nTraits\nResourceful and detail-oriented, team player, skilled problem-solver, multi-tasker, concise communicator,  dynamic team leader,  enthusiastic, ambitious and motivated.",
